latestIgtvVideos.title: Day Makeup Look
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hello everyone, My first ever video - a flawless and quick soft glam dewy day makeup look 💕
I hope you guys watch, enjoy and learn something out of it. Let me know in the comments below if you’ll would like to see more of these! 
Steps - 
1. @maccosmeticsindia fix plus spray 
2. Bobbi brown balm spf 25 
3. Moisturizer Propylene Glycol Cream 
4. Concealer @maccosmeticsindia Medium deep palette 
5. Foundation Makeup forever hd 
6. Filling the brows Pro hd brow palette 
7. Eyeshadow (lighter shade on the crease blend it then use a dark shade to build the colour and intensity) 
Huda beauty and Morphe palette 
8. Curling the lashes and adding mascara @tartecosmetics curler and @maybelline mascara 
9. Contouring tarte matte contour 
10. Blush on the cheeks O.two.O liquid blush 
11. Highlighter @bobbibrown 
12. Lipstick with some gloss @maybelline lipstick and @nykaabeauty Lip gloss 
#everydaymakeuplook #everydaymakeuptutorial #makeupbyjyotisamwani #naturalmakeup #dewymakeup
